=== Correct Function Usage ===
Functions execute in isolated scopes
--- Test 1: Simple function with parameters ---
add(5, 3) = 8
Expected: 8
--- Test 2: Function with local variables ---
Calculating area: 5 x 10
Area: 50
Expected: 50
--- Test 3: Function calling another function ---
